author: Jack Power, Jack Horgan-Jones
title: Coronavirus: 15 deaths reported in single Dublin nursing home
description: GP resigns from Medical Council after criticising State’s handling of nursing home outbreaks
content:
Fifteen patients have died from Covid-19 in a Dublin nursing home run by the Health Service Executive (HSE) which has been struggling to contain the virus in recent weeks.
